entry.title: Data Analysis Part One
entry.summary:
Data Analysis - Part One¶

This part we will use logistic regression and SVM model to analyze the dataset we get from Data Processing.

Import Libraries¶

<p>We can see that for variables "Urea Nitrogen", "Base Excess", "Creatinine", "icu_los", their increase usually increase the risk of death. And for varialbes "RDW", "Anion Gap", "White Blood Cells", their increase usually decrease the risk of death.</p>

    <div class="input_area">
<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1"># Predict function</span>

<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">death_risk_predict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Base_Excess</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">Anion_Gap</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">Chloride</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">Creatinine</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">Potassium</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">Sodium</span><span class="p">,</span> 
                       <span class="n">Urea_Nitrogen</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">RDW</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">White_Blood_Cells</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">icu_los</span><span class="p">):</span>
    
    <span class="c1">#Normalization</span>
    <span class="n">x1</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Base_Excess</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Base Excess'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Base Excess'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x2</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Anion_Gap</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Anion Gap'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Anion Gap'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x3</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Chloride</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Chloride'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Chloride'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x4</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Creatinine</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Creatinine'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Creatinine'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x5</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Potassium</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Potassium'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Potassium'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x6</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Sodium</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Sodium'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Sodium'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x7</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Urea_Nitrogen</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Urea Nitrogen'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'Urea Nitrogen'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x8</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">RDW</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'RDW'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'RDW'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x9</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">White_Blood_Cells</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'White Blood Cells'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'White Blood Cells'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">x10</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">icu_los</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'icu_los'</span><span class="p">])</span> <span class="o">/</span> <span class="n">max_min_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'icu_los'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    
    <span class="c1"># Predict</span>
    <span class="n">death_risk</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">model</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">predict_proba</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">np</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">array</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="n">x1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x2</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x3</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x4</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x5</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x6</span><span class="p">,</span> 
                                                  <span class="n">x7</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x8</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x9</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">x10</span><span class="p">])</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">))[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span>
    
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="nb">round</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">death_risk</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">)</span>
</pre></div>

<div class="inner_cell">

<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="c1"># Plot ROC function for web application</span>

<span class="n">ROC_logis_svm</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">pd</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">read_csv</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">'ROC_logis_svm.csv'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">AUC_dict</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="s1">'Logistic'</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="mf">0.77</span><span class="p">,</span>
            <span class="s1">'Linear_SVM'</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mf">0.77</span><span class="p">,</span>
            <span class="s1">'Poly_SVM'</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mf">0.79</span><span class="p">,</span>
            <span class="s1">'RBF_SVM'</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mf">0.75</span><span class="p">}</span>

<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">ROC_plot</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">model_name</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">model_name</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">'Logistic'</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">y_predict_proba</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ROC_logis_svm</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'y_logis_predict_proba'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="n">model_name</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">'Linear_SVM'</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">y_predict_proba</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ROC_logis_svm</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'y_linear_predict_proba'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="n">model_name</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">'Poly_SVM'</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">y_predict_proba</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ROC_logis_svm</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'y_poly_predict_proba'</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="n">model_name</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s1">'RBF_SVM'</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">y_predict_proba</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">ROC_logis_svm</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s1">'y_rbf_predict_proba'</span><span class="p">]</span>
        
    <span class="n">fpr</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">tpr</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">thresholds</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">metrics</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">roc_curve</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">y_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">y_predict_proba</span><span class="p">)</span>
    
    <span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">plot</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">fpr_rbf</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">tpr_rbf</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">label</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">'ROC curve (area = </span><span class="si">%0.2f</span><span class="s1">)'</span> <span class="o">%</span> <span class="n">AUC_dict</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">model_name</span><span class="p">])</span>
    <span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">xlabel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">'False Positive Rate'</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">ylabel</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">'True Positive Rate'</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">legend</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">loc</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"lower right"</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">title</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">'ROC for Radial Basis Function SVM'</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">plt</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">show</span><span class="p">()</span>         
</pre></div>
